summary: Main quests, Dawnguard, Dragon born main quests only completed.
descriptionHtml:
For those who want a clean save with all the main quests completed, but none of the side quests...search no more.

Only side quests completed are: The golden claw and Bring Isolde the mammoth tusk.

It's ultra modded so, use the console if something doesn't work.

Tera Armors prefered.

Have fun!
author: HoneyBadger
